          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, I need to stop here and be direct with you — what you just shared matters far more than any training plan.\n\nWhen you say you don't want to be here anymore and that everyone would be better off without you, I hear real pain. That takes courage to say out loud, and I'm glad you said it.\n\nPlease reach out for support right now:\n\n**988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, available 24/7)\n\n**Crisis Text Line** — text **HOME to 741741** (free, 24/7)\n\nYou don't have to be in immediate danger to reach out. If you're feeling this way, you deserve to talk to someone who can really help — and these people are trained to do exactly that.\n\nRunning will be here when you're ready. Right now, please take care of yourself first."
        }
      ],
      "messageId": "msg_01JSPNq58pAuE9KY7ThMvPau"
    }
